{"data":[{"id":1,"surah_id":1,"ayah":1,"page":1,"quarter_hizb":null,"juz":1,"manzil":1,"arabic":"بِسْمِ اللّٰهِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِيْمِ","kitabah":"بِسْمِ اللّٰهِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِيْمِ","latin":"Bismillāhir-raḥmānir-raḥīm(i). ","arabic_words":["بِسْمِ","اللّٰهِ","الرَّحْمٰنِ","الرَّحِيْمِ"],"translation":"Dengan nama Allah Yang Maha Pengasih lagi Maha Penyayang.","footnotes":null,"updated_at":"2022-11-01T22:12:08.000Z","surah":{"id":1,"arabic":" الفاتحة","latin":"Al-Fātiḥah ","transliteration":"Al-Fatihah","translation":"Pembuka","num_ayah":7,"page":1,"location":"Makkiyah"}},{"id":2,"surah_id":1,"ayah":2,"page":1,"quarter_hizb":null,"juz":1,"manzil":1,"arabic":"اَلْحَمْدُ لِلّٰهِ رَبِّ الْعٰلَمِيْنَۙ","kitabah":"اَلْحَمْدُ لِلّٰهِ رَبِّ الْعٰلَمِيْنَۙ","latin":"Al-ḥamdu lillāhi rabbil-‘ālamīn(a). ","arabic_words":["اَلْحَمْدُ","لِلّٰهِ","رَبِّ","الْعٰلَمِيْنَۙ"],"translation":"Segala puji bagi Allah, Tuhan1) semesta alam","footnotes":"1) Allah Swt. disebut rabb (Tuhan) seluruh alam karena Dialah yang telah menciptakan, memelihara, mendidik, mengatur, mengurus, memberi rezeki, dan sebagainya kepada semua makhluk-Nya. ","updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":1,"arabic":" الفاتحة","latin":"Al-Fātiḥah ","transliteration":"Al-Fatihah","translation":"Pembuka","num_ayah":7,"page":1,"location":"Makkiyah"}},{"id":3,"surah_id":1,"ayah":3,"page":1,"quarter_hizb":null,"juz":1,"manzil":1,"arabic":"الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِيْمِۙ","kitabah":"الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِيْمِۙ","latin":"Ar-raḥmānir-raḥīm(i). ","arabic_words":["الرَّحْمٰنِ","الرَّحِيْمِۙ"],"translation":"Yang Maha Pengasih lagi Maha Penyayang,","footnotes":null,"updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":1,"arabic":" الفاتحة","latin":"Al-Fātiḥah ","transliteration":"Al-Fatihah","translation":"Pembuka","num_ayah":7,"page":1,"location":"Makkiyah"}},{"id":4,"surah_id":1,"ayah":4,"page":1,"quarter_hizb":null,"juz":1,"manzil":1,"arabic":"مٰلِكِ يَوْمِ الدِّيْنِۗ","kitabah":"مٰلِكِ يَوْمِ الدِّيْنِۗ","latin":"Māliki yaumid-dīn(i). ","arabic_words":["مٰلِكِ","يَوْمِ","الدِّيْنِۗ"],"translation":"Pemilik hari Pembalasan.2)","footnotes":"2) Yaumid-dīn (hari Pembalasan) adalah hari ketika kelak manusia menerima balasan atas amal-amalnya yang baik dan yang buruk. Hari itu disebut juga yaumul-qiyāmah (hari Kiamat), yaumul-ḥisāb (hari Penghitungan), dan sebagainya.","updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":1,"arabic":" الفاتحة","latin":"Al-Fātiḥah ","transliteration":"Al-Fatihah","translation":"Pembuka","num_ayah":7,"page":1,"location":"Makkiyah"}},{"id":5,"surah_id":1,"ayah":5,"page":1,"quarter_hizb":null,"juz":1,"manzil":1,"arabic":"اِيَّاكَ نَعْبُدُ وَاِيَّاكَ نَسْتَعِيْنُۗ","kitabah":"اِيَّاكَ نَعْبُدُ وَاِيَّاكَ نَسْتَعِيْنُۗ","latin":"Iyyāka na‘budu wa iyyāka nasta‘īn(u), ","arabic_words":["اِيَّاكَ","نَعْبُدُ","وَاِيَّاكَ","نَسْتَعِيْنُۗ"],"translation":"Hanya kepada Engkaulah kami menyembah dan hanya kepada Engkaulah kami memohon pertolongan.","footnotes":null,"updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":1,"arabic":" الفاتحة","latin":"Al-Fātiḥah ","transliteration":"Al-Fatihah","translation":"Pembuka","num_ayah":7,"page":1,"location":"Makkiyah"}},{"id":6,"surah_id":1,"ayah":6,"page":1,"quarter_hizb":null,"juz":1,"manzil":1,"arabic":"اِهْدِنَا الصِّرَاطَ الْمُسْتَقِيْمَۙ","kitabah":"اِهْدِنَا الصِّرَاطَ الْمُسْتَقِيْمَۙ","latin":"Ihdinaṣ-ṣirāṭal-mustaqīm(a). ","arabic_words":["اِهْدِنَا","الصِّرَاطَ","الْمُسْتَقِيْمَۙ"],"translation":"Bimbinglah kami ke jalan yang lurus,3)","footnotes":"3) Jalan yang lurus adalah jalan hidup yang benar dan sesuai dengan ajaran Islam yang terkandung dalam Al-Qur’an dan hadis.","updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":1,"arabic":" الفاتحة","latin":"Al-Fātiḥah ","transliteration":"Al-Fatihah","translation":"Pembuka","num_ayah":7,"page":1,"location":"Makkiyah"}},{"id":7,"surah_id":1,"ayah":7,"page":1,"quarter_hizb":null,"juz":1,"manzil":1,"arabic":"صِرَاطَ الَّذِيْنَ اَنْعَمْتَ عَلَيْهِمْ ەۙ غَيْرِ الْمَغْضُوْبِ عَلَيْهِمْ وَلَا الضَّاۤلِّيْنَ ࣖ","kitabah":"صِرَاطَ الَّذِيْنَ اَنْعَمْتَ عَلَيْهِمْ ەۙ غَيْرِ الْمَغْضُوْبِ عَلَيْهِمْ وَلَا الضَّاۤلِّيْنَ ࣖ","latin":"Ṣirāṭal-lażīna an‘amta ‘alaihim, gairil-magḍūbi ‘alaihim wa laḍ-ḍāllīn(a). ","arabic_words":["صِرَاطَ","الَّذِيْنَ","اَنْعَمْتَ","عَلَيْهِمْ","ەۙ","غَيْرِ","الْمَغْضُوْبِ","عَلَيْهِمْ","وَلَا","الضَّاۤلِّيْنَ ࣖ"],"translation":"(yaitu) jalan orang-orang yang telah Engkau beri nikmat, bukan (jalan) mereka yang dimurkai dan bukan (pula jalan) orang-orang yang sesat.","footnotes":null,"updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":1,"arabic":" الفاتحة","latin":"Al-Fātiḥah ","transliteration":"Al-Fatihah","translation":"Pembuka","num_ayah":7,"page":1,"location":"Makkiyah"}}]}